### 1. Start the Backend
\`\`\`bash
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
\`\`\`
*(The SQLite database `database.db` will automatically generate on the first run).*

### 2. Run the Test Suite
\`\`\`bash
cd backend
npm run test
\`\`\`

### 3. Start the Frontend
Open a new terminal tab:
\`\`\`bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
\`\`\`
*(Ensure `.env` contains `VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:3000`)*

